title: #92Noon Vox in the Box 2019!  Boudreau/Carter/Russo/LaPanta
description: #92Noon is live from the Xcel Energy Center for our annual Vox in the Box show!  PA & Nordo are joined by Tenna B, Bruce Boudreau, Ryan Carter, Michael Russo, & Anthony LaPanta for plenty of hockey talk, with a little football and basketball mixed in!
